I"}<p>udaan is a B2B ecommerce platform that brings traders, wholesalers, distributors, retailers, and manufacturers in India on to a single platform. Our goal is to make ‘doing business’ easy in India &amp; make B2B commerce convenient and efficient.</p>
<p>udaan Capital is the NBFC arm of Udaan &amp; offers credit services to buyers and sellers on and off udaan’s B2B ecommerce platform to grow their business further. This space is largely untapped with less than 10% of MSMEs having access to working capital loans from financial institutions. In this way, udaan is uniquely positioned to formalize &amp;scale trade credit.</p>
